{
  "stem": "945.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, at that time, we really didn't know yet what-- what was in store for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember having to wear a star yet in Vyshnivets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it would be soon enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We soon enough found out that-- what the plans for us were, when one day they announced that all Jewish people from Vyshnivets-- because the Jewish people from the surrounding areas were sent off to Yedinitz.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was earlier.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yedinitz.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think, was anywhere on the outskirts of Bessarabia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm just not sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was on the border between Bucovina and Bessarabia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm glad that I mentioned Yedinitz, because that's where my grandfather on my father's side, [NON-ENGLISH], and his wife [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Vicki, ?] and my aunt [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Henja, ?] the youngest one in the family, youngest sister of my dad, they were taken away with all the other Jewish people that lived in the surrounding areas of Vyshnivets in the smaller villages and the smaller towns.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Marched to Yedinitz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know-- I remember saying goodbye to my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember just like yesterday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They didn't know where they were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't know where they were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't know what their fate would be.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And here, we say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Lived a lifetime together, and all of a sudden, you say goodbye, and they're gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "All we heard after they left was that apparently, they had been all gathered in the area, and they were made to suffer something about water not being available for them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That there was only one well to supply water to all these people, and the Romanians soldiers in charge would not give them any water unless they gave their valuables.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We heard about that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
